Name: Looking Up I See Only A Ceiling
About the game: A seemingly monotonous life, full of books and endless study. But what happens if you reach the 'point of no return'? Follow the challenging life of a student in this short psychological adventure game. Short but meaningful experience; Hand drawn locations and characters; 3 endings to discover; An unlockable mode to know more about the game's lore.
